data.description: You'll love this cozy, Cape Cod-style home located at the end of a one-way street. Home has 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, and full, dry basement. Enjoy viewing nature on your wooden deck that leads out to a large, private, wooded backyard. Home boasts a new sump pump, updated bathtub plumbing, and newer furnace. If you are looking for single-floor living and craving a clean, low maintenance property this home is for you!
